About us
About
Maison & Jardin
Who
We Are
Maison & Jardin is the ideal place for your special event or wedding in Orlando.
Since 1958, we have been providing Central Florida with the most memorable venues, complete with stunning ambiance and unparalleled service.
Our spaces come complete with full catering and professional chefs, plus an experienced staff that is committed to making your dream event come true. And with a perfect five-star rating on WeddingWire and The Knot, you can trust us to turn all of your wedding planning wishes into reality.
Make your next event an unforgettable moment at Maison & Jardin.
Maison
And Jardin
a storied history 
rich in elegance.
The Renovated rustic French provincial event spaces at Maison & Jardin have been making dreams come true since 1958 – no other venue in Orlando Florida has such a storied history!
Our elegant interior and exterior spaces offer timelessness, perfect for any occasion – from weddings to corporate conventions and retreats.
With 24 years of experience and a locally-owned facility, you’ll have peace of mind for your event planning needs.
